Buffalo Narrows Airport (IATA: YVT, ICAO: CYVT) is located 2 NM (3.7 km; 2.3 mi) east-southeast of Buffalo Narrows, Saskatchewan, Canada.
Courtesy Air (formerly called Buffalo Narrows Airways Ltd.) is based out of the airport, where it operates its maintenance facilities and provides scheduled flights from Lloydminster and to Key Lake Airport and Collins Bay Airport.Voyage Air maintains a base at the airport, including hangar and maintenance facilities for its Turbo Otter and DeHavilland Beaver.